      <title>特朗普关税担忧导致宝马、保时捷领跌德国汽车股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/bmw-porsche-lead-german-auto-stock-rout-on-trump-tariff-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫后美国将提高进口汽车关税，宝马汽车公司和保时捷汽车公司领跌德国汽车制造商股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/bmw-porsche-lead-german-auto-stock-rout-on-trump-tariff-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 10:59:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选结果：唐纳德·特朗普接近击败哈里斯 | 彭博社《脉搏》 11/06/24</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/trump-trade-on-amid-election-results-the-pulse-11-06-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[所谓的“特朗普交易”正在如火如荼地进行着，彭博美元指数和美国股指期货创下新高。唐纳德·特朗普即将重新夺回白宫，他被预测将在关键战场州获胜，他的政党将控制参议院，市场对他可能获胜的预期也随之波动。特朗普在佛罗里达州西棕榈滩举行的选举观察会上向支持者发表讲话，称这是“我们国家前所未有的政治胜利”。共和党还赢得了美国参议院的控制权，至少在俄亥俄州和西弗吉尼亚州翻转了席位，同时成功抵御了德克萨斯州和内布拉斯加州的挑战。

今天的嘉宾：Chatham House 的 Leslie Vinjamuri；Nuveen Asset Management 首席信息官 Saira Malik；Novo Nordisk 首席财务官 Karsten Munk Knudsen；Actum 的 Morris Reid（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/trump-trade-on-amid-election-results-the-pulse-11-06-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 10:58:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选改变利率押注 欧元平价重回舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/euro-parity-back-in-play-as-trump-win-spurs-rates-divergence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统竞选中的胜利增加了欧洲大幅降息的可能性，从而推动欧元与美元平价，货币交易员开始看空欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/euro-parity-back-in-play-as-trump-win-spurs-rates-divergence</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 10:53:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银和法国农业信贷银行在欧盟债券卡特尔罚款纠纷中败诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ubs-credit-agricole-lose-court-fight-over-eu-bond-cartel-fines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士信贷的新东家瑞银集团和法国农业信贷银行因竞争对手银行之间的债券交易卡特尔而被欧盟法院裁定罚款数百万欧元，但最终败诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ubs-credit-agricole-lose-court-fight-over-eu-bond-cartel-fines</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 08:57:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选引发本能反应，信贷风险下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/credit-markets-send-some-of-their-most-bullish-signals-in-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管唐纳德·特朗普的总统任期可能会受到关税和可能的贸易战的影响，但信贷风险因特朗普赢得美国总统选举而下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/credit-markets-send-some-of-their-most-bullish-signals-in-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:47:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税风险冲击欧元、德国汽车股；可再生能源下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/european-stock-futures-drop-over-tariff-worries-as-trump-leads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的总统胜利加剧了人们对全面关税的担忧，欧元创下了四年多以来的最大单日跌幅，而汽车制造商等对美国收入依赖较大的行业表现不佳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/european-stock-futures-drop-over-tariff-worries-as-trump-leads</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:44:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战担忧再起，特朗普贸易重创新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/emerging-currencies-slump-as-markets-lean-toward-a-trump-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的当选引发了“特朗普交易”的复苏并导致新兴市场下滑，墨西哥引领了货币崩溃，而中国则引发了股市抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/emerging-currencies-slump-as-markets-lean-toward-a-trump-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 03:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赢得大选，美元创一年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/dollar-rises-to-highest-since-july-as-polls-close-in-key-states</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选，美元升至一年来的最高水平，因市场猜测他的政策将使美国利率维持在高位，引发美国国债收益率大幅上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/dollar-rises-to-highest-since-july-as-polls-close-in-key-states</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 02:21:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选提振美元 大宗商品下跌 贸易局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强以及唐纳德·特朗普担任总统期间可能出现的贸易争端将削弱原材料在全球市场上的吸引力，大宗商品价格普遍下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</guid>
